edu.xtec.jclic.clic3

Class Clic3Pac

  • java.lang.Object
    • edu.xtec.jclic.clic3.Clic3
      • edu.xtec.jclic.clic3.Clic3Pac

  • public class Clic3Pac
extends Clic3
    This class encapsulates a Clic 3.0 package of activities (.pac file), and provides methods to import it from a data stream and to import it into a JClicProject.
    Version:
    13.08.08
    Author:
